Value Filldown VLAN_ID (\d+)
Value Filldown VLAN_NAME (.+?)
Value TAGGED (.+)
Value UNTAGGED (.+)
Value ROUTER_INTERFACE (\d+)

Start
  ^vlan\s+${VLAN_ID}\s+name\s+${VLAN_NAME}\s+by\s+port
  ^vlan\s+${VLAN_ID}\s+by\s+port
  ^\s+tagged\s+${TAGGED} -> Record
  ^\s+untagged\s+${UNTAGGED} -> Record
  ^\s+router-interface\s+ve\s+${ROUTER_INTERFACE} -> Record
